<%# Extracted so PackagesController#update_item can refresh this badge alongside
    the edited row (see update_item.turbo_stream.erb) — otherwise, saving the
    LAST incomplete item's customs would complete the package but leave this
    header badge stuck showing "incomplete" until the modal is reloaded from
    scratch, since the row-edit turbo_stream only replaces the one <tr>. %>
<span id="<%= dom_id(package, :customs_status) %>">
  <% unless package.customs_complete? %>
    <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-amber-100 text-amber-800">
      <%= t("packages.customs_fields.incomplete") %>
    </span>
  <% end %>
</span>
